Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…正在從空中墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議…為什麼不覺得害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…是哪裏呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄、暖融融的 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心頭覺得很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不覺得害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的 不過 還是謝謝你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.46,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「繭·從空中落下的夢·Old Home」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可…不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(年幼組不准進入！！——礫)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到了 快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已經來了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從鎮上到這裏還真遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫的機車又只能一個人騎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(年幼組不准進入！！——礫)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是會起反效果嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(繭生成地區！ 禁止進入！)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 明明都已經寫了不准進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們還是進來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經說過不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 對啊 讓我們看一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不回去 我就要扁你們了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫你啊 太寵孩子們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 工作那邊…你們可以請假嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 這對我們「灰羽」來說 可是件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能錯過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以休假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天起 大概有三天左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回的主角在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好大哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的很壯觀啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡得太遲了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要翹班過來很不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初應該只是如蒲公英花絨般的大小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看看成長的過程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要更細心留意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是偶然被礫發現 或許就這樣直接孵化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我們五個人 怎麼可能留意到這龐大建築的每個角落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這麼個龐然大物 不想注意到也難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面轉變為灰色了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許不用多久 就會孵化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先把這個房間打掃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是在這雜物間般的地方出生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有人在這裏面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 無論是空還是我 所有的灰羽都是這樣誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好大的怪物蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還在這裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物 怪物～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間絕對禁止進入哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…小鬼們都那麼興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己才是最興奮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很高興吧 我也同樣期待新夥伴的到來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空也很期待哦 如果像妹妹一樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～這個繭比空的大多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃了 打掃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你捉弄我～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像夢還在繼續一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到…聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變乾淨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用抽籤來決定輪班的順序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 用鐵錘什麼的把它弄破不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 這是慣例
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不靠自己的力量破繭 就無法成長為堅強的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是小雞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪班睡著看守就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不叫輪班值守了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛「崩」地一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲的…裏面…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在做奇怪的夢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬梆梆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夢裏面 分明是軟棉棉的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有樹種般的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍微外出買了些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡了一整天呢 好驚人～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了應該讓我留守的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光你不是要負責光輪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}覺得怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}肚子會不會餓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}我還以為是中午呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}現在需要些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要同時說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會聽不清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 亂哄哄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫礫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏雖然是我的房間\N不過也像是客廳一樣 你就隨意使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把客房當成自己的房間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我要搬了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我就從頭說起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以抽煙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 首先說說你所見到的夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你看到了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在繭中沉睡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 是可怕的夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…好像是 從非常高的地方筆直往下墜落的夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？名字會衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時候 做的是輕飄飄地漂浮在空中的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有了「空」這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「灰羽」是以在繭中所見之夢來命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢是在純白的亮光之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:11:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫作「光」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢見像魚一樣在河裏游動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是河裏的魚 「河魚」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她呢 是在夢中也一直睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極有睡覺天分的瞌睡蟲「眠」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外呢 還有什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有看到什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落…落下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就用「墜落而下」的「落下」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「落下」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你過去是什麼人 已經無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然這也包括你自身在內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落下同志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為「灰羽」的證明 以及對你未來的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授予你這個光輪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還很燙 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合適 很合適啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 過個兩三天後就會固定住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 午休結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是先打個照面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天等你長出翅膀 我們會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候再好好聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫 那麼接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落下 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算安靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多的時候 總是不太方便說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要從哪裏開始說起呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請問 這裏是哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「灰羽」是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之後 你的也會長出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後有不適感嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點…我想是不是在哪裏撞到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿冰塊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐著別動 只是先做些準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 翅膀成長的速度 似乎比想像中來得快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該在發燒之前 先把各種事情向你說個明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是痛…不如說好像要被撕裂了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀從身體冒出時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會很痛 然後突然發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要睡一晚就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡…鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看比較好 看了反而更會覺得痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…不是人類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們究竟是何物 無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 被稱為「灰羽」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「灰羽」是無法從這個城鎮離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就算這個地方有你的家人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他們見到了現在的你 我想也是認不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你無法回憶起過去所在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的任何人也不曾記得你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…就是這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有任何優點 應該只是個平凡的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人記得理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬住這個 小心別咬到舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腳又冰又沉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當肩膀和腋下感到痛楚時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的翅膀被牽連著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到翅膀漸漸成為了身體的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像自己的身體被改造了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗流進了眼睛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都…看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫 你在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的翅膀變得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直…在弄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很花時間的哦 若不把血跟油漬清洗乾淨 會留有污痕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手…沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？小事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想著自己的事情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就會好了哦 讓人無法置信般地痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的翅膀很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不白也不黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的灰色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜電體質？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…我不記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的是這光輪啦…能夠弄好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礫 難道在我睡著之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還一直在為我清理翅膀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 變漂亮了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 歡迎來到我們的「Old Home」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:45.37,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}なぜ 忘れたいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:51.35,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ねえ 思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:22:03.02,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あたたかい頬に降る 涙の願い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:09.62,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}なぜ ふるえながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:15.18,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}今 求めあうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:21.81,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}君だけを何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:27.50,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}抱きしめたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:33.88,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蒼い星の海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:39.76,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波間に漂う羽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.82,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}消えてゆく哀しみは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:51.40,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}明日への祈りなの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:56.25,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Blueflow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:45.37,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}為何想要忘卻？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:51.35,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}請回想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:22:03.02,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那溫暖的臉頰上滑落而下的淚之請願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:09.62,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}為何你在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:15.18,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}現在尋求著何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:21.81,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}只有你無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:27.50,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}都想與你相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:33.88,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蔚藍的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:39.76,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波浪間漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.82,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}漸漸逝去的悲痛是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:51.40,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向著明日的祈禱

